gedly%20orchestrating%20a%20failed%20plot%20to%20kill%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%20residing%20in%20New%20York%20City.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ex-officer%2C%20previously%20associated%20with%20the%20Research%20and%20Analysis%20Wing%20(RAW)%2C%20is%20accused%20of%20coordinating%20an%20assassination%20attempt%20on%20Pannun%2C%20a%20dual%20US-Canadian%20citizen.%20The%20US%20Justice%20Department%20has%20charged%20him%20with%20murder-for-hire%20and%20money%20laundering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20FBI%20will%20not%20tolerate%20acts%20of%20violence%20or%20other%20efforts%20to%20retaliate%20against%20those%20residing%20in%20the%20U.S.%20for%20exercising%20their%20constitutionally%20protected%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20FBI%20Director%20Christopher%20Wray%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plot%20allegedly%20began%20in%20May%202023%2C%20with%20the%20former%20officer%2C%20then%20reportedly%20an%20employee%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20allegedly%20collaborating%20with%20individuals%20in%20India%20and%20overseas%20to%20execute%20the%20assassination.%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20the%20intended%20target%2C%20is%20a%20designated%20terrorist%20in%20India%20and%20an%20advocate%20for%20Khalistan%2C%20a%20proposed%20independent%20Sikh%20homeland%20to%20be%20carved%20out%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Reuters%2C%20the%20ex-officer%20remains%20in%20India%2C%20but%20American%20officials%20are%20expected%20to%20pursue%20his%20extradition%20to%20face%20charges%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlot%20Details%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20RAW%20officer%20is%20accused%20of%20recruiting%20an%20Indian%20national%2C%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20to%20execute%20the%20assassination.%20Mr%20Gupta%20was%20arrested%20in%20Prague%20last%20June%2C%20after%20travelling%20from%20India%2C%20and%20subsequently%20extradited%20to%20the%20US%2C%20where%20he%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%20to%20the%20charges.%20The%20indictment%20describes%20how%20Mr%20Gupta%20was%20hired%20to%20%26quot%3Borchestrate%20the%20assassination%20of%20the%20victim%20in%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20authorities%20argue%20that%20Mr%20Gupta%20felt%20there%20was%20urgency%20in%20killing%20Pannun%2C%20particularly%20after%20the%20murder%20of%20another%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20in%20Canada%20in%202023.%20According%20to%20the%20indictment%2C%20Mr%20Gupta%20believed%20that%20after%20Nijjar's%20killing%2C%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bnow%20no%20need%20to%20wait%26quot%3B%20for%20Pannun's%20assassination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20indictment%2C%20the%20ex-officer%20and%20Mr%20Gupta%20allegedly%20contracted%20an%20individual%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20killing%20for%20%24100%2C000.%20The%20FBI%20later%20discovered%20that%20the%20hired%20assassin%20was%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20an%20FBI%20informant%20working%20undercover.%20In%20June%202023%2C%20just%20days%20before%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20state%20visit%20to%20the%20US%2C%20the%20informant%20received%20a%20%2415%2C000%20advance%20for%20the%20murder%20from%20the%20ex-officer%20and%20Mr%20Gupta.%20The%20transaction%20reportedly%20took%20place%20in%20a%20car%20in%20New%20York%2C%20and%20a%20photograph%20of%20the%20exchange%20has%20been%20included%20in%20the%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20indictment%20also%20includes%20an%20alleged%20photograph%20of%20the%20ex-officer%20in%20military%20attire.%20The%20prosecutors%20allege%20that%20the%20former%20officer%20instructed%20Mr%20Gupta%20and%20the%20hired%20assassin%20to%20delay%20the%20killing%20until%20after%20PM%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20avoid%20diplomatic%20fallout%20during%20the%20high-profile%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20few%20minutes%20later%2C%20(the%20officer)%20messaged%20Gupta%2C%20instructing%3A%20'Let%20them%20also%20verify%20by%20their%20own...%20if%20they%20are%20able%20to%20get%20some%20proof%20that%20he%20is%20inside...%20it%20will%20be%20a%20go%20ahead%20from%20us%2C'%26quot%3B%20the%20indictment%20reads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Completely%20Unwarranted'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20yesterday%20confirmed%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bindividual%26quot%3B%20named%20in%20the%20US%20Justice%20Department's%20indictment%20is%20no%20longer%20associated%20with%20the%20Indian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20State%20Department%20informed%20us%20that%20the%20individual%20in%20the%20Justice%20Department%20indictment%20is%20no%20longer%20employed%20by%20India.%20I%20confirm%20that%20he%20is%20no%20longer%20an%20employee%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20State%20Department%20Spokesperson%20Matthew%20Miller%20yesterday%20confirmed%20that%20the%20Indian%20delegation%20had%20met%20with%20an%20inter-agency%20team%20from%20the%20FBI%2C%20Department%20of%20Justice%2C%20and%20the%20State%20Department.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20satisfied%20with%20the%20cooperation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Miller%20told%20reporters.%20%26quot%3BIt%20continues%20to%20be%20an%20ongoing%20process.%20We%20continue%20to%20work%20with%20them%20on%20that%2C%20but%20we%20do%20appreciate%20the%20cooperation%2C%20and%20we%20appreciate%20them%20updating%20us%20on%20their%20investigation%20as%20we%20update%20them%20on%20ours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%20this%20year%2C%20a%20US%20court%20issued%20a%20summons%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%20over%20Pannun's%20civil%20suit%2C%20alleging%20a%20plot%20to%20murder%20him.%20The%20Indian%20government%20labelled%20the%20summons%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20unwarranted%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20summons%20had%20named%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%2C%20former%20R%26amp%3BAW%20chief%20Samant%20Goel%2C%20along%20with%20the%20former%20officer%20and%20Mr%20Gupta%20and%20sought%20a%20reply%20within%2021%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20Secretary%20Vikram%20Misri%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20these%20issues%20were%20first%20brought%20to%20our%20attention%2C%20we%20took%20action.%20There's%20a%20high-level%20committee%20engaged%20(in%20this%20matter).%20I%20invite%20your%20attention%20to%20the%20person%20who%20filed%20this.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729226340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fd10hkbbo_pannun3_625x300_18_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fex-indian-spy-charged-in-us-over-alleged-khalistani-terrorist-murder-plot-report-6815072%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20United%20States%20has%20charged%20a%20former%20Indian%20intelligence%20officer%20for%20allegedly%20orchestrating%20a%20failed%20plot%20to%20kill%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%20residing%20in%20New%20York%20City.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Will%20Replace%20Yahya%20Sinwar%3F%20These%20Top%20Hamas%20Leaders%20Are%20In%20Contention%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-israeli-military-tracked-and-killed-hamas-chief-yahya-sinwar-in-gaza-6814828%5C%22%3EYahya%20Sinwar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Hamas%20leader%20who%20orchestrated%20the%20October%202023%20assault%20on%20Israel%20and%20eluded%20capture%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year%2C%20was%20killed%20by%20Israeli%20forces%20yesterday%20in%20southern%20Gaza.%20Sinwar%2C%2061%2C%20had%20spent%20two%20decades%20in%20Israeli%20prisons%20before%20returning%20to%20Gaza%20and%20emerging%20as%20its%20top%20leader.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20one%20of%20the%20chief%20architects%20of%20the%20surprise%20October%207%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20which%20killed%20over%201%2C200%20Israelis%20and%20brought%20more%20than%20250%20hostages%20into%20Gaza%2C%20Sinwar%20was%20a%20prime%20Israeli%20target.%20Israel%20had%20placed%20a%20%24400%2C000%20bounty%20on%20information%20leading%20to%20his%20capture%20or%20death.%20Despite%20numerous%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20targeting%20Hamas%20leadership%2C%20Sinwar%20managed%20to%20survive%20underground%20for%20months%20in%20the%20maze%20of%20tunnels%20beneath%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWATCH%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdrone-footage-of-hamas-chief-yahya-sinwars-last-moments-released-by-israel-6815660%5C%22%3EDrone%20Footage%20Of%20Hamas%20Chief%20Yahya%20Sinwar's%20Last%20Moments%20Released%20Bu%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinwar's%20death%20now%20leaves%20a%20power%20vacuum%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20Hamas%2C%20raising%20questions%20about%20who%20will%20step%20in%20to%20fill%20the%20void%20during%20this%20crucial%20phase%20of%20the%20Gaza%20war.%20Several%20high-ranking%20Hamas%20figures%2C%20all%20with%20long%20histories%20of%20militant%20operations%20and%20political%20manoeuvring%2C%20are%20potential%20successors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20look%20at%20the%20figures%20who%20may%20lead%20Hamas%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMahmoud%20al-Zahar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahmoud%20al-Zahar%2C%20one%20of%20Hamas's%20founding%20members%20is%20a%20frontrunner%20to%20succeed%20Sinwar.%20Known%20for%20his%20hardline%20stance%2C%20even%20by%20Hamas's%20standards%2C%20al-Zahar%20was%20instrumental%20in%20shaping%20the%20group's%20ideological%20framework%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20both%20militant%20resistance%20against%20Israel%20and%20Islamist%20governance%20in%20Gaza.%20Al-Zahar%20also%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20the%20group's%20rise%20to%20power%20following%20the%202006%20Palestinian%20legislative%20election%20and%20served%20as%20its%20first%20foreign%20minister.%3