a%20company%20memo%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fsama%2Fstatus%2F1839096160168063488%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshared%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20September%2025%2C%20Altman%20wrote%20the%20departure%20was%20amicable.%20He%20also%20announced%20a%20leadership%20change%20that%20will%20give%20him%20at%20least%20six%20direct%20reports.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20hasn't%20explicitly%20said%20that%20he's%20taking%20on%20an%20interim%20role%20as%20CTO%3B%20he%20did%20say%20in%20the%20memo%20that%20he%20would%20spend%20most%20of%20his%20time%20%26quot%3Bon%20the%20technical%20and%20product%20parts%20of%20the%20company.%26quot%3BAn%20unnamed%20source%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Ffeatures%2F2024-openai-executives%2F%3Fsrnd%3Dprognosis%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Altman%20wouldn't%20seek%20a%20replacement%20CTO%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20corporate%20management%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Altman%20risks%20stretching%20himself%20too%20thin%20by%20serving%20as%20CEO%20and%20the%20public%20face%20of%20the%20company%20while%20moving%20forward%20without%20a%20chief%20technology%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20that's%20a%20smart%20move%2C%26quot%3B%20Peer%20Fiss%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20management%20and%20organization%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Southern%20California%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Fiss%20said%20he%20often%20focuses%20on%20high-profile%20matters%20of%20corporate%20governance%2C%20including%20OpenAI%2C%20Apple%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-twitter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk's%20Twitter%20purchase%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20MBA%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CTO%2C%20a%20role%20most%20commonly%20seen%20at%20tech%20firms%2C%20ensures%20that%20a%20company's%20technology%20strategy%20is%20aligned%20with%20the%20organization's%20goals.%20Fiss%20said%20it%20would%20be%20concerning%20if%20Altman%20were%20to%20move%20on%20without%20a%20CTO%20because%20the%20chief%20executive%20job%20is%20already%20demanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatricia%20Lenkov%2C%20a%20founder%20of%20Agility%20Executive%20Search%20who%20said%20she%20has%20helped%20large%20financial%20firms%2C%20including%20JPMorgan%2C%C2%A0find%20a%20CTO%2C%C2%A0said%20that%20Altman%20should%20only%20keep%20the%20CTO%20role%20vacant%20on%20an%20interim%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOften%20in%20this%20case%2C%20a%20CEO%20and%20the%20board%20will%20take%20the%20opportunity%20to%20really%20think%20through%20the%20new%20configuration%20of%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Lenkov%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%20that%20they're%20a%20%24157%20billion%20valuation%20company%2C%20they%20need%20different%20kinds%20of%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20founding%20in%202015%2C%20OpenAI%20has%20assumed%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-openai-needs-to-do-to-become-for-profit-altman-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehybrid%20governance%20structure%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20which%20a%20nonprofit%20board%20controls%20the%20startup's%20for-profit%20arm.%20This%20structure%20allows%20for%20some%20investor%20return%20while%20ensuring%20the%20company%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edoesn't%20stray%20from%20its%20stated%20mission%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-mission-drift-for-profit-nonprofit-structure-investment-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebenefit%20all%20of%20humanity.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReuters%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Fopenai-remove-non-profit-control-give-sam-altman-equity-sources-say-2024-09-25%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20September%20that%20the%20startup%20wanted%20to%20eliminate%20the%20nonprofit's%20control