nt%2Ftamil%2Fmovies%2Fbox-office%2Fvettaiyan-box-office-collection-day-8-rajinikanth-amitabh-bachchans-film-mints-rs-3-15-crore%2Farticleshow%2F114331565.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Netanyahu%20Says%20Yahya%20Sinwar%20Killing%20%26quot%3BBeginning%20Of%20End%26quot%3B%20Of%20Gaza%20War%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20said%20Thursday%20that%20the%20killing%20of%20Hamas%20chief%20Yahya%20Sinwar%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bbeginning%20of%20the%20end%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20year-long%20war%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20said%20that%20after%20a%20lengthy%20hunt%2C%20troops%20had%20on%20Wednesday%20%26quot%3Beliminated%20Yahya%20Sinwar%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Hamas%20terrorist%20organisation%2C%20in%20an%20operation%20in%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20Strip%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20has%20not%20confirmed%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%2C%20who%20vowed%20to%20crush%20Hamas%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20war%2C%20hailed%20Sinwar's%20killing%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BWhile%20this%20is%20not%20the%20end%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20it's%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20earlier%20called%20Sinwar's%20death%20an%20%26quot%3Bimportant%20landmark%20in%20the%20decline%20of%20the%20evil%20rule%20of%20Hamas%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20of%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20October%207%20attack%20that%20sparked%20the%20war%2C%20Sinwar%20became%20the%20militant%20group's%20overall%20leader%20after%20the%20killing%20in%20July%20of%20its%20political%20chief%2C%20Ismail%20Haniyeh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20said%20to%20have%20masterminded%20the%20October%207%20attack%2C%20the%20deadliest%20in%20Israeli%20history%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%201%2C206%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilia