who%20is%20responsible%20for%20that%20very%20difficult%20day%20a%20year%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20vowed%20the%20military%20would%20keep%20fighting%20%26quot%3Buntil%20we%20capture%20all%20the%20terrorists%20involved%20in%20the%20October%207%20massacre%20and%20bring%20all%20the%20hostages%20home%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20Israelis%20hailed%20the%20news%20of%20Sinwar's%20death%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20better%20things%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20celebrating%20the%20death%20of%20Sinwar%2C%20who%20has%20brought%20us%20nothing%20but%20harm%2C%20who%20has%20taken%20people%20hostage%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20Israeli%20woman%2C%20Hemda%2C%20who%20only%20gave%20her%20first%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttending%20a%20Tel%20Aviv%20rally%20demanding%20the%20hostages'%20release%2C%2060-year-old%20Sisil%2C%20who%20also%20gave%20only%20her%20first%20name%2C%20said%20his%20killing%20presented%20a%20%26quot%3Bonce%20in%20a%20lifetime%20opportunity%26quot%3B%20for%20%26quot%3Ba%20hostage%20deal%20to%20end%20the%20war%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20whether%20the%20Hamas%20chief's%20death%20will%20bring%20the%20end%20of%20the%20war%20any%20closer%20is%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWarning%20that%20the%20hostages%20were%20in%20%26quot%3Bgrave%20danger%26quot%3B%2C%20Israeli%20military%20historian%20Guy%20Aviad%20said%20Sinwar's%20killing%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20significant%20event...%20but%20it's%20not%20the%20end%20of%20the%20war%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECampaign%20group%20the%20Hostages%20and%20Missing%20Families%20Forum%20urged%20the%20Israeli%20government%20and%20international%20mediators%20to%20leverage%20%26quot%3Bthis%20major%20achievement%20to%20secure%20hostages'%20return%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20statement%20from%20Netanyahu's%20office%2C%20Biden%20called%20him%20to%20congratulate%20him%20on%20Sinwar's%20killing%2C%20with%20the%20two%20leaders%20vowing%20to%20seize%20%26quot%3Ban%20opportuni