EIsrael%20has%20hailed%20the%20death%20of%20the%2061-year-old%20Sinwar%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20blows%20it%20has%20dealt%20Hamas%20since%20the%20Gaza%20war%20started%20with%20the%20group's%20October%207%2C%202023%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20%26quot%3Bconfirms%20that%20after%20a%20year-long%20pursuit%2C%20yesterday%20(Wednesday)%2C%20October%2016%2C%202024%2C%20IDF%20(military)%20soldiers%20from%20the%20Southern%20Command%20eliminated%20Yahya%20Sinwar%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Hamas%20terrorist%20organisation%2C%20in%20an%20operation%20in%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20dozens%20of%20operations%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20IDF%20and%20the%20ISA%20(Shin%20Bet%20internal%20security%20agency)%20over%20the%20last%20year%2C%20and%20in%20recent%20weeks%20in%20the%20area%20where%20he%20was%20eliminated%2C%20restricted%20Yahya%20Sinwar's%20operational%20movement%20as%20he%20was%20pursued%20by%20the%20forces%20and%20led%20to%20his%20elimination%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIDF%20soldiers%20of%20the%20828th%20Brigade%20(Bislach)%20operating%20in%20the%20area%20identified%20and%20eliminated%20three%20terrorists.%20After%20completing%20the%20process%20of%20identifying%20the%20body%2C%20it%20can%20be%20confirmed%20that%20Yahya%20Sinwar%20was%20eliminated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20later%20statement%2C%20military%20spokesman%20Rear%20Admiral%20Daniel%20Hagari%20said%20Sinwar%20was%20killed%20after%20being%20spotted%20with%20two%20other%20fighters%20in%20the%20territory's%20Rafah%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20forces%20idenfitied%20three%20terrorists%20who%20were%20going%20from%20home%20to%20home%20on%20the%20run%2C%26quot%3B%20Hagari%20told%20a%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETroops%20engaged%20the%20group%2C%20forcing%20Sinwar%20to%20flee%20as%20the%20group%20dispersed%20after%20being%20shot.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSinwar%20ran%20away%20alone%20into%20one%20of%20the%20buildings%20and%20our%20forces%20scanned%20the%20area%20with%20a%20drone%20%E2%80%93%20which%20you%20can%20see%20in%20this%20film%20--%20Yahya%20Sinwar%20injured%20his%20hand%20in%20the%20shooting%2C%20who%20can%20be%20seen%20here%20covered%20with%20his%20face%2C%20he%20threw%20a%20branch%20at%20the%20drone%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hagari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20No%20hostages%20with%20Sinwar%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrone%20footage%20released%20by%20the%20military%20showed%20Sinwar%20alone%20in%20a%20blown-up%20apartment%2C%20with%20one%20hand%20severly%20injured%20and%20head%20covered%20in%20a%20traditional%20scarf%2C%20throwing%20a%20stick%20at%20the%20approaching%20drone%20during%20his%20final%20moments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20identified%20him%20as%20a%20terrorist%20inside%20a%20building%20and%20we%20shot%20into%20the%20building%20and%20we%20entered%20to%20scan%20the%20area.%20We%20found%20him%20with%20a%20gun%20and%2040%20thousand%20shekels.%20He%20was%20on%20the%20run%20and%20our%20forces%20eliminated%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hagari.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNear%20the%20terrorists%20we%20eliminated%20were%20no%20hostages%20and%20our%20forces%20are%20now%20screening%20the%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20accuses%20Sinwar%20of%20being%20the%20mastermind%20of%20the%20October%207%20attacks%20along%20with%20Hamas%20military%20chief%20Mohammed%20Deif.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20said%20Deif%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20strike%20earlier%20this%20year%20though%20the%20Palestinian%20group%20has%20not%20confirmed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinwar%20in%20August%20replaced%20Hamas's%20former%20chief%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%2C%20who%20was%20killed%20in%20Iran%20on%20July%2031.%20Israel%20has%20not%20commented%20on%20Haniyeh's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hamas%20attack%20last%20ye