rk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EGrubhub%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20meal%20perk%20is%20meant%20to%20support%20Meta%20employees%20at%20locations%20where%20free%20meals%20aren't%20provided%20by%20a%20cafeteria%2C%20or%20when%20employees%20work%20into%20the%20evening.%20Those%20who%20violated%20the%20policy%20used%20the%20%2425%20credit%20to%20order%20other%20items%2C%20including%20laundry%20detergent%2C%20wine%20glasses%2C%20and%20acne%20pads%2C%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20situation%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Not%20everyone%20who%20misused%20the%20perk%20was%20fired%2C%20the%20person%20said%20%E2%80%94%20only%20those%20who%20had%20demonstrated%20a%20pattern%20of%20abusing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20on%20the%20forum%20said%20they%20weren't%20aware%20Meta%20would%20strictly%20enforce%20the%20policy%20and%20expressed%20concern%20about%20potentially%20violating%20other%20company%20policies%20without%20knowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20action%20instills%20fear%20in%20employees%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20employee%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BAnyone%20can%20violate%20a%20policy%20by%20mistake.%20It's%20like%20taking%20away%20your%20driving%20license%20because%20you%20were%20going%2055%20instead%20of%2050.%20I%20challenge%20anyone%20to%20say%20that%20they%20know%20ALL%20the%20policies%20this%20company%20has.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20employee%20was%20less%20sympathetic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20weird%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThey%20violated%20a%20'follow%20this%20rule%20or%20you%20will%20be%20terminated'%20policy%2C%20and%20they%20were%20terminated.%20There%20is%20nothing%20to%20worry%20about%20unless%20you%20are%20also%20violating%20company%20policies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rules%20you%20need%20to%20follow%20to%20keep%20your%20job%20are%20all%20written%20out%20for%20you.%20Read%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Meta%20employee%20wrote%20on%20the%20forum%20that%20they%20had%20used%20their%20Grubhub%20credit%20for%20a%20laid-off%20worker%20and%20received%20a%20%26quot%3Bwarning%20email.%26quot%3B%20Then%2C%20they%20said%20they%20were%20terminated%20within%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20Grubhub%20account%20got%20deactivated%20first%20and%20then%20my%20intern%20account%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20employee%20said%20in%20the%20forum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20Meta%20employee%20referenced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-year-of-efficiency-working-meta-ai-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMark%20Zuckerberg's%20%26quot%3Byear%20of%20efficiency%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20strategy%20in%20assessing%20the%20recent%20firings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20Meta%20still%20thinks%20itself%20a%20large%20company%20of%20small%20entrepreneurship%2C%20with%20the%20'year(s)%20of%20efficiency%2C'%20it's%20starting%20to%20take%20policy%20noncompliance%20of%20employees%20more%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShould%20folks%20%5Bhave%5D%20done%20a%20better%20risk%20assessment%20for%20their%20%2425%20dinners%3F%20Likely%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20employee%20added.%20%26quot%3BShould%20Meta%20have%20requested%20the%20employee%20refund%20the%20company%2C%20put%20a%20block%20on%20the%20benefit%2C%20and%20delivered%20a%20one-more-strike-of-any-kind-you-are-out%20warning%3F%20Probably.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20drew%20a%20connection%20between%20the%20firings%20and%20recent%20layoffs.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-reorganized-major-businesses-eliminated-roles-whatsapp-instagram-reality-labs-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20company%20announced%20on%20Wednesday%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20reorganized%20some%20of%20its%20biggest%20businesses%2C%20including%20Instagram%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20and%20Reality%20Labs%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20some%20role%20eliminations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3