p%3E%3Cp%3EAustin%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defense.gov%2FNews%2FReleases%2FRelease%2FArticle%2F3937640%2Fstatement-by-secretary-of-defense-lloyd-j-austin-iii-on-us-airstrikes-in-houthi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20operation%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20was%20a%20unique%20demonstration%20of%20the%20United%20States'%20ability%20to%20target%20facilities%20that%20our%20adversaries%20seek%20to%20keep%20out%20of%20reach%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20deeply%20buried%20underground%2C%20hardened%2C%20or%20fortified.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227360%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20B-2%20bomber%20against%20a%20solid%20gray%20sky.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a1534d80d4d5da13d6e00b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224912%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20B-2%20Spirt%20in%20the%20sky%20over%20northwest%20Missouri%20in%20August%202018.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20National%20Guard%20photo%20by%20Senior%20Master%20Sgt.%20Vincent%20De%20Groot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20defense%20secretary%20said%20that%20using%20the%20B-2s%20in%20the%20strike%20operation%20demonstrates%20America's%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20strike%20capabilities%20to%20take%20action%20against%20these%20targets%20when%20necessary%2C%20anytime%2C%20anywhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20operation%20marks%20the%20first%20known%20deployment%20of%20the%20B-2%20in%20the%20US%20military's%20monthslong%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-stuck-red-sea-battle-cant-fight-houthis-forever-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecounter-Houthi%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20during%20which%20the%20Pentagon%20has%20relied%20heavily%20on%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-aircraft-carrier-eisenhower-planes-in-air-constantly-houthis-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewarships%20and%20fighter%20jets%3C%2Fa