2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fsettled-its-account-israeli-pm-on-hamas-leader-yahya-sinwars-killing%2Famp_articleshow%2F114327595.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fsettled-its-account-israeli-pm-on-hamas-leader-yahya-sinwars-killing%2Famp_articleshow%2F114327595.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20hot%20new%20longevity%20treatment%20for%20aging%20athletes%20and%20CEOs%20is%20a%20plasma%20exchange%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225616%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20container%20of%20blood%20plasma%20is%20being%20extracted%20from%20a%20centrifuge%20for%20a%20medical%20procedure%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670edbcd6ac7b701e7cbe62c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223744%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESpinning%20blood%20in%20a%20centrifuge%20to%20remove%20the%20plasma%20can%20treat%20certain%20medical%20conditions%2C%20and%20some%20doctors%20are%20exploring%20the%20benefits%20for%20longevity%20too.%20%3Cp%3Eozina%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPlasma%20exchange%20therapy%20is%20gaining%20popularity%20as%20a%20wellness%20trend%20among%20longevity-seekers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20procedure%20involves%20replacing%20plasma%20to%20remove%20toxins%2C%20typically%20from%20specific%20health%20conditions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere's%20limited%20evidence%20it%20can%20boost%20longevity%20or%20benefit%20otherwise%20healthy%20people.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20medical%20treatment%20used%20for%20health%20emergencies%20and%20autoimmune%20disorders%20is%20becoming%20the%20hot%20new%20wellness%20trend%20for%20CEOs%2C%20athletes%2C%20and%20other%20longevity-seekers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBryan%20Johnson%2C%20a%20CEO%20and%20entrepreneur%20known%20for%20his%20strict%20longevity%20regimen%20and%20exploration%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstem-cell-injections-knee-joints-longevity-wellness-industry-bryan-johnson-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperimental%20antiaging%20treatments%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20recently%20posted%20on%20X%20about%20his%20experience%20with%20plasmapheresis%2C%20or%20plasma%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20procedure%20involves%20gradually%20removing%20small%20amounts%20of%20blood%20and%20spinning%20it%20in%20a%20centrifuge.%20That%20separates%20the%20plasma%20from%20the%20red%20blood%20cell%20in%20order%20to%20remove%20it%20and%20replace%20it%20with%20another%20fluid%2C%20such%20as%20albumin%2C%20a%20protein%20in%20plasma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20wellness%20clinic%2C%20it%20can%20cost%20from%20%245%2C000%20to%20more%20than%20%2410%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXPrize%20founder%20Peter%20Diamandis%20has%20tried%20it.%20So%20has%20former%20NFL%20star%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnfl-hall-of-famer-troy-aikman-follows-pegan-diet-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETroy%20Aikman%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bessentially%20a%20human%20oil%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Jonathann%20Kuo%2C%20a%20regenerative%20medicine%20specialist%20and%20founder%20of%20Extension%20Health%2C%20performed%20Aikman's%20plasma%20exchange.%20He%20told%20Business%20Insider%20it%20helps%20remove%20toxins%2C%20some%20related%20to%20aging%2C%20that%20accumulate%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20call%20it%20an%20oil%20change%20because%20it%20is%20kind%20of%20refreshing%20and%20revitalizing%20your%20circulation%20and%20getting%20rid%20of%20all%20of%20the%20dirty%20stuff%20that's%20circulating%2C%20basically%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKuo%20said%20it's%20part%20of%20a%20suite%20of%20cutting-edge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhuman-life-span-plateaued-what-you-can-do-long-life-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eantiaging%20therapies%3C%2Fa%3E%20offered%20at%20his%20clinic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlasma%20exchange%20can%20improve%20certain%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-the-maximum-age-of-humans-115-or-older-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeasures%20of%20aging%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20at%20least%20in%20the%20short%20term%2C%20according%20to%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F33191466%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanimal%20studies%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Conboy%20Laboratory%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley.%20The%20same%20researchers%20found%20similar%20potential%20antiaging%20benefits%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC9398900%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Every%20small%20exploratory%20study%20on%20humans%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20major%20risk%20of%20serious%20side%20effects%2C%20though%20infection%20can%20occur%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20clear%20that%20plasma%20exchange%20is%20beneficial%20for%20most%20healthy%20people%2C%20according%20to%20Dr.%20Brian%20Adkins%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20pathology%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Texas%20Southwestern%20Medical%20Center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdkins%20performs%20plasma%20exchanges%20regularly%20to%20help%20patients%20with%20chronic%20conditions%20such%20as%20autoimmune%20disorders.%20He%20said%20the%20treatment%20is%20also%20used%20in%20serious%20circumstances%20such%20as%20organ%20failure%20or%20sepsis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22109ebfd5-b3eb-4eca-a26d-676eae4aeea0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20you%20get%20a%20plasma%20exchange%20for%20longevity%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPlasma%20exchange%20therapy%20is%20typically%20used%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1002%2Fjca.22043%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especific%20conditions%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Guillain-Barre%20Syndrome%2C%20and%20is%20reserved%20for%20more%20extreme%20cases%2C%20Dr.%20Ryan%20Marino%2C%20a%20toxicologist%20and%20professor%20of%20emergency%20medicine%20at%20Case%20Western%20Reserve%20University%20School%20of%20Medicine%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20faced%20some%20backlash%20from%20medical%20experts%20on%20X%20for%20seemingly%20commodifying%20a%20treatment%20that%20can%20be%20crucial%20for%20people%20with%20chronic%20illnesses%2C%20or%20life-saving%20in%20emergencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20supposed%20to%20be%20boutique%20medicine%3B%20it's%20supposed%20to%20be%20evidence-based%20medicine%2C%26quot%3B%20Adkins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUndergoing%20plasma%20treatment%20at%20a%20longevity%20clinic%20may%20not%20make%20sense%20for%20several%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%2C%20people%20who%20aren't%20experiencing%20organ%20failure%20or%20other%20life-threatening%20medical%20conditions%20naturally%20remove%20toxins%20are%20naturally%20via%20the%20liver%20and%20kidneys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlasma%20exchange%20is%20also%20unlikely%20to%20help%20remove%20environmental%20contaminants%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicroplastics-penises-testicles-male-fertility-plastic-health-environment-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emicroplastics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20growing%20concern%20for%20long-term%20health%20since%20the%20procedure%20involves%20plastic%20bags%20and%20tubing%2C%20and%20the%20components%20are%20exposed%20to%20plastics%20during%20processing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20a%20misconception%20that%20plasma%20exchange%20completely%20replaces%20the%20plasma%20since%20some%20amount%20needs%20to%20continue%20circulating%20in%20your%20body%20while%20you're%20alive%2C%20like%20changing%20your%20oil%20while%20the%20car%20is%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20what%20we%20know%20about%20the%20safety%20and%20potential%20benefits%20of%20plasma%20exchange%20comes%20from%20data%20on%20people%20who%20donate%20plasma%20%E2%80%94%20which%20not%20only%20doesn't%20cost%20anything%2C%20you%20can%20even%20get%20paid%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERemoving%20plasma%20can%20lower%20a%20person's%20lipid%20levels%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ftreatments%2Fhigh-cholesterol%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bbad%26quot%3B%20cholesterol%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20this%20is%20temporary%20because%20plasma%20regenerates%20quickly%2C%20which%20is%20why%20it%20can%20be%20safely%20removed%20or%20donated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarino%20and%20Adkins%20said%20the%20interest%20in%20plasma%20exchanges%20for%20longevity%20is%20part%20of%20an%20enduring%20fascination%20with%20cleansing%20our%20bodies%20from%20toxins%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20ancient%20times%20and%20antique%20procedures%20like%20bloodletting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20sounds%20plausible%20that%20cleaning%20your%20blood%20or%20plasma%20would%20provide%20benefits%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20believe%20that%20there%20are%20such%20toxins%20circulating%20that%20could%20be%20removed%2C%26quot%3B%20Marino%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20interested%20in%20living%20a%20longer%2C%20healthier%20life%2C%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquick-life-hacks-increase-longevity-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escience-based%20longevity%20strategies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20eating%20a%20nutritious%20diet%2C%20getting%20regular%20exercise%2C%20and%20sleeping%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20really%20meaningful%20things%20you%20can%20do%20to%20improve%20your%20health.%20Maybe%20people's%20efforts%20might%20be%20better%20served%20exploring%20some%20of%20those%20inventions%2C%26quot%3B%20Adkins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-plasma-exchange-therapy-why-is-it-longevity-treatment-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3