0a%20long%20time.%20Most%20lenders%20wanted%20to%20settle%20but%20one%20or%20two%20wanted%20to%20make%20a%20killing%20out%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Raveendran%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20Byju's%20is%20undergoing%20insolvency%20proceedings%2C%20triggered%20after%20the%20BCCI%20approached%20the%20National%20Company%20Law%20Appellate%20Tribunal%20to%20recover%20its%20Rs%20158.9-crore%20dues.%20The%20company%20settled%20the%20dispute%20with%20BCCI%20after%20paying%20the%20entire%20dues%20following%20which%20NCLAT%20revoked%20the%20insolvency%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20US%20lenders%20through%20their%20agent%20Glas%20Trust%20challenged%20the%20NCLAT%20order%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20which%20restored%20the%20insolvency%20proceedings%20against%20the%20edtech%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EByju's%20has%20raised%20a%20%241.2%20billion%20Term%20Loan%20B%20(TLB)--%20a%20loan%20which%20is%20issued%20by%20institutional%20investors%20--through%20its%20holding%20company%20Byju's%20Alpha%2C%20from%20US-based%20lenders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trouble%20for%20Think%20and%20Learn%2C%20which%20owns%20the%20Byju's%20brand%2C%20began%20after%20the%20lenders%20through%20Glas%20Trust%20approached%20Delaware%20Court%20of%20Chancery%20alleging%20default%20in%20the%20payments%20under%20the%20loan%20agreement%20and%20sought%20early%20payment%20of%20the%20%241.2-billion%20TLB.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US-based%20lenders%20through%20Glas%20have%20filed%20claims%20of%20%241.35%20billion%20dues%20in%20Indian%20courts%20during%20ongoing%20insolvency%20proceedings%20against%20the%20edtech%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20latest%20statement%2C%20the%20lenders%20have%20raised%20their%20total%20claim%20to%20%241.5%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raveendran%20said%20that%20no%20money%20raised%20from%20US%20lenders%20has%20come%20to%20India%20as%20it%20also%20needs%20permission%20from%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20there%20are%20some%20aggressive%20lenders%20who%20initiated%20a%20case%20against%20the%20company%20and%20they%20don't%20care%20about%20stakeholders%20in%20the%20business%20as%20it%20is%20their%20business%20model%20to%20make%20money%20out%20of%20distress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raveendran%20said%20that%20all%20the%20deals%20and%20acquisitions%20were%20approved%20by%20the%20Byju's%20board%2C%20which%20included%20leading%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20acquisitions%20were%20brought%20in%20by%20the%20investors%20and%20we%20got%20carried%20away.%20Investors%20wanted%20us%20to%20launch%20in%2040%20countries%20together.%20Investors%20celebrated%20when%20we%20raised%20a%20%241.2-billion%20loan%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Raveendran%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EByju's%20board%20member%20representing%20Peak%20XV%20Partners%2C%20earlier%20known%20as%20Sequoia%20Capital%20India%2C%20Prosus%20and%20Chan%20Zuckerberg%20Initiative%20resigned%20from%20the%20company%20in%20June%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raveendran%20said%20that%20investors%20resigned%20from%20the%20board%20after%20Glas%20Trust%20filed%20a%20case%20in%20the%20Delaware%20court%20assuming%20that%20the%20liability%20to%20pay%20back%20the%20loan%20would%20fall%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%2C%20over%20the%20years%2C%20only%20managers%20have%20left%20the%20company%20and%20five%20out%20of%20six%20owners%20of%20Byju's%20are%20still%20with%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raveendran%20said%20that%20he%20is%20hopeful%20of%20making%20a%20big%20comeback%20after%20the%20insolvency%20issue%20is%20resolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20subsidiary%20has%20not%20taken%20any%20hits.%20At%20a%20consolidated%20level%2C%20we%20will%20have%20more%20than%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore%20in%20revenue.%20We%20are%20struggling%20in%20the%20core%20business%20which%20has%20become%20zero.%20Still%2C%20there%20are%20200%20million%20kids%20who%20come%20to%20our%20platform%20every%