%2C%20generally%2C%20first-year%20students%20are%20victims%20but%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20by%20the%20third-year%20student%20against%20final-year%20students%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729189620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-12%2Fbullying-ragging_650x400_51482299619.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbeaten-for-not-removing-clothes-kanpur-student-files-case-against-8-seniors-6813805%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20FIR%20was%20registered%20on%20Thursday%20against%20eight%20final-year%20engineering%20students%20of%20Harcourt%20Butler%20Technical%20University%20(HBTU)%20on%20the%20charge%20of%20attempt%20to%20murder%20for%20allegedly%20beating%20their%20juniors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbeaten-for-not-removing-clothes-kanpur-student-files-case-against-8-seniors-6813805%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amazon%2C%20Google%2C%20Microsoft%20looking%20at%20N-power%20for%20emission-free%20electricity%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729189031000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Famazon-google-microsoft-looking-at-n-power-for-emission-free-electricity-124101701635_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Microsoft%2C%20Google%20and%20Amazon%20have%20recently%20struck%20deals%20with%20operators%20and%20developers%20of%20nuclear%20power%20plants%20to%20fuel%20the%20boom%20in%20data%20centres%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Famazon-google-microsoft-look