2Opposition%20Reaches%20Consensus%20On%20263%20Maharashtra%20Seats%2C%2025%20Disputed%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20elections%20just%20over%20a%20month%20away%2C%20the%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20has%20firmed%20up%20seat%20sharing%20on%20263%20of%20the%20state's%20288%20Assembly%20constituencies%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20meeting%20of%20alliance%20partners%20Congress%2C%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP%20and%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20was%20held%20on%20Thursday%20and%20good%20progress%20was%20made%20in%20seat-sharing%20discussions%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%20The%20meeting%20was%20attended%20by%20Congress%20Maharashtra%20President%20Nana%20Patole%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20MP%20Sanjay%20Raut%20and%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20leaders%20Jitendra%20Awhad%2C%20Jayant%20Patil%20and%20Anil%20Deshmukh%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remaining%2025%20seats%20which%20remain%20disputed%20include%20five%20of%20the%2036%20Assembly%20constituencies%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20including%20Kurla%2C%20Dharavi%2C%20Versova%20and%20Byculla.%20The%20sources%20said%20the%20list%20of%20finalised%20and%20disputed%20segments%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20the%20heads%20of%20the%20other%20two%20coalition%20partners%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20who%20will%20take%20a%20final%20decision%20in%20%26quot%3Btwo%20to%20three%20days%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20announced%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20Maharashtra%20polls%20will%20be%20held%20in%20a%20single%20phase%20on%20November%2020%2C%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20one%20of%20the%20most%20interesting%20Assembly%20contests%20the%20state%20has%20ever%20seen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShifting%20Equations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20election%20in%202019%20was%20a%20fairly%20straightforward%20battle%20between%20the%20ruling%20BJP-Shiv%20Sena%20coalition%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20and%20the%20Congress-NCP%20alliance%20on%20the%20other.%20Despite%20having%20the%20numbers%20to%20form%20the%20government%20after%20the%20results%20were%20declared%2C%20the%20BJP-Shiv%20Sena%20alliance%20split%20over%20the%20chief%20minister's%20post%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20took%20the%20top%20job%20in%20the%20state%20after%20forging%20a%20coalition%20with%20the%20NCP%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20were%20seen%20as%20unlikely%20partners.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20rebellion%20by%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20Eknath%20Shinde%20led%20to%20the%20government%20falling%20in%202022%20and%20Mr%20Shinde%20went%20on%20to%20take%20oath%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20with%20the%20BJP's%20support.%20The%20ruling%20alliance%20got%20a%20third%20partner%20the%20following%20year%20when%20Ajit%20Pawar%20decided%20to%20split%20the%20NCP%20and%20took%20oath%20as%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20alongside%20BJP%20leader%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contest%20now%20is%20between%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20two%20Shiv%20Senas%20and%20NCPs%2C%20whose%20leaders%20are%20out%20to%20prove%20they%20are%20the%20real%20claimants%20of%20the%20original%20parties'%20legacies%20despite%20the%20original%20symbols%20and%20names%20going%20to%20the%20rebel%20factions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELok%20Sabha%20Results%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20jolted%20the%20ruling%20coalition%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Mahayuti%2C%20when%20it%20won%20just%2017%20of%20the%20state's%2048%20constituencies%20while%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi's%20tally%20was%2030.%20The%20Assembly%20elections%20were%2C%20thus%2C%20seen%20as%20an%20uphill%20battle%20for%20the%20Mahayuti%20but%20appear%20to%20have%20been%20made%20easier%20by%20the%20results%20of%20the%20polls%20in%20Haryana%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20formed%20a%20government%20-%20delivering%20its%20best-ever%20performance%20in%20the%20state%20-%20despite%20battling%20anti-incumbency%20after%20two%20straight%20terms%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20was%20criticised%20by%20its%20allies%2C%20including%20Mr%20Thackeray's%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20over%20the%20Haryana%20loss%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20elections%20in%20the%20northern%20state%20would%20not%20have%20a%20bearing%20on%20the%20Maharashtra%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20studying%20the%20Haryana%20results%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%20look%20at%20the%20results%20of%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Assembly%20elections.%20I%20do%20not%20think%20that%20it%20(Haryana%20results)%20will%20have%20any%20bearing%20on%20the%20state's%20elections.%20As%20far%20as%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20concerned%2C%20the%20world%20community%20gives%20more%20attention%20to%20it%20and%20its%20poll%20results%20are%20more%20important%20for%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Conference-Congress%20Alliance%20won%2048%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%2080%20constituencies%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20state's%20first%20Assembly%20elections%20since%202014.%20The%20Congress%20contributed%20only%20six%20of%20these%2C%20however%2C%20and%20decided%20to%20extend%20support%20to%20the%20government%20from%20outside%20after%20the%20Omar%20Abdullah-led%20party%20received%20the%20backing%20of%20four%20Independents%20and%20the%20lone%20AAP%20MLA.%20Sources%20had%20said%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20after%20the%20Congress%20was%20offered%20only%20one%20ministerial%20berth.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729187220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fqm7vralo_maha-vikas-aghadi-leaders_625x300_17_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.n