%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20clear%20CSAT%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20focussing%20solely%20on%20Maths%20and%20Logical%20Reasoning.%20I%20neglected%20the%20English%20comprehension%20section%20and%20even%20avoided%20questions%20that%20seemed%20doable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20an%20aspirant%2C%20we%20should%20not%20forget%20that%20UPSC%20tests%20your%20abilities%20in%20every%20section.%20You%20cannot%20choose%20to%20opt-out%20of%20topics%20that%20you%20are%20not%20comfortable%20with.%20In%20my%20third%20attempt%2C%20I%20set%20my%20ego%20aside%20and%20gave%20equal%20weight%20to%20all%20three%20sections.%20That%20is%20what%20UPSC%20expects%20%E2%80%94%20do%20not%20neglect%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20overcome%20the%20challenges%20presented%20by%20this%20crucial%20component%20of%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F362685%2Fhow-to-clear-upsc-cse-from-home-irms-officer-akash-chavda-prep-journey-delhi-coaching-busting-myths%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20UPSC%20examination%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Karamveer%20strategically%20adjusted%20his%20preparation%20approach.%20He%20dedicated%20about%20three%20hours%20of%20study%20each%20day%20for%20three%20months%20to%20excel%20in%20this%20section.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20merely%20attempting%20more%20comprehension%20questions%20was%20not%20enough.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20times%2C%20questions%20on%20basics%20like%20permutations%20and%20combinations%2C%20profit%20and%20loss%2C%20and%20percentages%20are%20designed%20to%20challenge%20even%20IIT%20students.%20To%20ace%20both%20Maths%20and%20Logical%20Reasoning%2C%20I%20started%20referring%20to%20notes%20meant%20for%20the%20CAT%20(Common%20Admission%20Test)%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaramveer%20also%20began%20analysing%20the%20last%2010%20years%E2%80%99%20question%20papers%20and%20their%20answer%20keys.%20This%20analysis%20helped%20him%20under