rooms%20in%20collaboration%20with%20LEAD%20Group%2C%20academics%20is%20no%20longer%20limited%20to%20the%20textbook.%20Teacher%20Divya's%20classroom%20is%20one%20example%20of%20this%20%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-4-1727934307.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-4-1727934307-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-4-1727934307-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-4-1727934307-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-4-1727934307-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368497%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20the%20integration%20of%20smart%20TVs%20in%20classrooms%20in%20collaboration%20with%20LEAD%20Group%2C%20academics%20is%20no%20longer%20limited%20to%20the%20textbook.%20Teacher%20Divya%E2%80%99s%20classroom%20is%20one%20example%20of%20this%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20smart%20TVs%20in%20classrooms%2C%20digital%20tablets%20with%20pre-loaded%20lesson%20plans%20and%20tools%20for%20teachers%2C%20and%20school%20excellence%20kits%20that%20couple%20audio-visual%20learning%20with%20a%20kinesthetic%20approach%2C%20the%20duo%20is%20certain%20that%20learning%20is%20set%20to%20touch%20new%20horizons.%20Head%20Nandan%20testifies%20to%20this.%20%E2%80%9CA%20smart%20and%20interactive%20learning%20environment%20is%20created%20for%20the%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20they%20loving%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes!%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20Tanushree%2C%20a%20primary%20student.%20Today%2C%20she%20is%20particularly%20thrilled%20as%20her%20favourite%20fable%20%E2%80%98Magic%20Pot%E2%80%99%20got%20a%20whole%20new%20meaning%20through%20the%20audio-visual%20content.%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%20see%20everything%20that%20is%20in%20my%20textbook%20and%20also%20watch%20it%20happening!%20I%20love%20learning%20phonics%2C%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sumeet%20and%20Smita%20set%20out%20to%20transform%20the%20educational%20landscape%20in%20India%20with%20an%20ambition%20to%20reshape%20classroom%20dynamics%2C%20their%20focus%20lay%20on%20tier%20two%2C%20three%2C%20and%20four%20towns.%20And%20this%20calculated%20decision%20has%20been%20rewarding.%20Today%2C%20LEAD%20Group%20is%20present%20in%20over%208%2C000%20schools%2C%20and%20the%20duo%20shares%20that%20each%20of%20these%20schools%20has%20witnessed%20palpable%20changes%20once%20they%20have%20embraced%20technology-driven%20multimodal%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FnrD91f4BFew%3Fsi%3DhATfIMm-7Zkpip25%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20rewards%20has%20been%20improved%20student%20mastery%20across%20all%20subjects%20%E2%80%93%20students%20become%20fluent%20in%20English%2C%20and%20do%20better%20in%20Math%20and%20Science.%20Drawing%20from%20this%2C%20Smita%20shares%20the%20model%20that%20has%20worked%20in%20their%20favour%3B%20one%20that%20involves%20all%20stakeholders%20%E2%80%94%20principals%2C%20teachers%2C%20parents%2C%20and%20students%3B%20thereby%20embedding%20sustainable%20change%20within%20the%20school%E2%80%99s%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20numbers%20are%20telling.%20But%20the%20real%20validation%20lies%20in%20heartwarming%20stories%20that%20Smita%20and%20Sumeet%20hear%20every%20now%20and%20then.%20Letting%20us%20in%20on%20one%20such%20anecdote%2C%20Smita%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20teacher%20who%20once%20took%20the%20LEAD%20tab%20in%20her%20hand%20and%20called%20it%20her%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eshikshan%20mitra%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(teacher%E2%80%99s%20friend).%20The%20reason%20for%20calling%20it%20this%2C%20the%20teacher%20went%20on%20to%20explain%2C%20was%20that%20the%20device%20guided%20her%2C%20taught%20her%20what%20to%20do%2C%20and%20gave%20her%20insights%20about%20her%20students.%20It%20was%20everything%20she%20needed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaking%20barriers%20and%20overcoming%20odds%20are%20central%20to%20these%20success%20stories%20you%E2%80%99ve%20just%20read.%20As%20the%20day%20wears%20on%2C%20a%20slight%20drizzle%20announces%20the%20arrival%20of%20dusk.%20Karnataka%20gears%20up%20for%20what%20promises%20to%20be%20a%20heavy%20downpour.%20Shops%20in%20the%20area%20down%20their%20shutters%2C%20and%20Ishwargowda%20Patil%20is%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-6-1727934739.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ishwargowda%20Basavanagowda%20Patil%20has%20a%20thriving%20field%20of%20green%20gram%20that%20he%20cultivates%20once%20he%20has%20wrapped%20up%20his%20kirana%20shop%20operations%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-6-1727934739.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-6-1727934739-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-6-1727934739-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-6-1727934739-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3