use%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%2018%20%E2%80%94%20beautiful%2C%20witty%2C%20and%20popular.%20Her%20dream%20of%20becoming%20a%20social%20media%20influencer%20was%20quickly%20becoming%20a%20reality%2C%20with%201.42%20lakh%20followers%20on%20Instagram.%20But%20in%20June%20this%20year%2C%20her%20life%20took%20a%20tragic%20turn%20when%20she%20died%20by%20suicide.%20A%20Class%2012%20student%2C%20she%20battled%20for%20her%20life%20in%20the%20hospital%20for%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20police%20reports%2C%20she%20had%20become%20the%20target%20of%20cyber%20trolls%20following%20a%20breakup%20with%20her%20boyfriend%2C%20who%20was%20later%20arrested.%20Sadly%2C%20this%20young%20girl%20from%20Kerala%20did%20not%20survive.%20Her%20story%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F238152%2Fyoutube-report-teachers-social-media-internet-trolls-comments-online-classes-sexual-abuse-delhi-kerala-opinion-ser106%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efar%20from%20isolated%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20one%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20venture%20into%20the%20dark%20web%20to%20witness%20the%20horrors%20of%20the%20internet%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20if%20one%20is%20a%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20morphed%20my%20picture%20into%20nudes%20and%20created%20a%20fake%20profile.%20When%20I%20first%20found%20out%2C%20I%20was%20worried%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priya%20Lalwani%2C%20who%20works%20at%20an%20edtech%20firm%2C%20shares.%20%E2%80%9COh%20my%20god%2C%20this%20is%20not%20me!%20What%20if%20my%20parents%20see%3F%20What%20if%20they%20found%20out%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritha%20Sarkar%2C%20who%20works%20as%20an%20assistant%20professor%20at%20a%20university%20in%20Odisha%20was%20terrorised%20by%20Facebook%20notifications%20during%20her%20PhD%20in%20Kanpur.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20time%20I%20opened%20Facebook%2C%20there%20were%20hundreds%20of%20notifications.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98How%20much%20do%20you%20charge%20for%20a%20night%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20(along%20with%20cuss%20words%20and%20other%20profanities)%20made%20up%20most%20of%20the%20notifications%20Pritha%20received.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20hell!%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20I%20did%20wrong.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20why%20I%20was%20being%20slut%20shamed%20and%20targeted%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pritha%20shares.%20Her%20only%20mistake%20was%20sharing%20a%20cartoon%20depicting%20a%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20at%20the%20beach%2C%20where%20the%20man%20says%20to%20the%20woman%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20dress%20properly%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20about%20to%20get%20married%20and%20needed%20to%20work%20on%20my%20papers%2C%20but%20I%20was%20traumatised.%20Imagine%20waking%20up%20to%20over%20a%20hundred%20notifications%2C%20most%20of%20which%20questioned%20your%20character%20%E2%80%94%20how%20would%20you%20feel%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NCRB%20data%2C%20cybercrime%20cases%20in%20India%20rose%20significantly%2C%20jumping%2063.48%25%20from%2027%2C248%20in%202018%20to%2044%2C548%20in%202019.%20This%20trend%20continued%20with%20a%20further%20increase%20of%2012.32%25%20in%202020.%20Additionally%2C%20a%20UNICEF%20poll%20revealed%20that%20over%2033%25%20of%20young%20people%20across%2030%20countries%20have%20reported%20being%20victims%20of%20online%20bullying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENirali%20Bhatia%2C%20along%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20Ritesh%20Bhatia%2C%20have%20been%20helping%20victims%20of%20cyberbullying%20since%202016%20and%20elaborates%20on%20the%20problem.%20Together%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F179257%2Fmumbai-couple-troll-police-cyberbullying-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethey%20run%20CYBER%20B.A.A.P%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20an%20acronym%20for%20%E2%80%9CCyberbullying%20Awareness%2C%20Action%2C%20and%20Prevention%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20their%20brainchild%2C%20a%20not-for-profit%20organisation%20registered%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Niralibhatia%20Cyber%20Wellness%20Foundation%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHonestly%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20specific%20redressal%20mechanism%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F107128%2Ffreedom-of-speech-in-the-age-of-twitter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecyberbullying%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20per%20se%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20pointing%20out%20two%20of%20the%20major%20challenges%20women%20may%20face%20when%20trying%20to%20fight%20cyberbullying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNumber%20one%2C%20we%20are%20not%20aware%20of%20all%20the%20sections%20it%20%5Bcyberbullying%5D%20falls%20under%2C%20or%20how%20to%20report%20it.%20Number%20two%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20guilt%20and%20shame%20associated.%20Because%20even%20police%20professionals%20are%20not%20yet%20sensitised%20towards%20these%20kinds%20of%20crimes.%20The%20first%20question%20is%2C%20%E2%80%98Why%20did%20you%20even%20click%20a%20picture%20like%20this%3F%E2%80%99%20That%20itself%20takes%20you%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nirali%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Pritha%2C%20both%20these%20roadblocks%20were%20a%20reality.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20small%20issue%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20just%20young%20guys%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls%20the%20communication%20she%20received%20when%20she%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20cyber%20crime%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20I%20did%20not%20know%20what%20to%20do.%20I%20really%20had%20no%20clue.%20But%20I%20was%20losing%20sleep%3B%20I%20began%20losing%20some%20confidence.%20I%20was%20in%20a%20bad%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pritha%20recalls%3B%20she%20pauses%2C%20perhaps%20trying%20to%20subdue%20the%20trauma%20that%20some%20men%2C%20hiding%20behind%20computers%2C%20scarred%20her%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20husband%2C%20who%20was%20my%20then%20partner%2C%20was%20the%20one%20who%20told%20me%20that%20this%20is%20cyberbullying%20and%20that%20I%20can%20lodge%20a%20complaint%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CI%20followed%20up%20(with%20the%20cyber%20department)%20for%20three%20months%2C%20but%20nothing%20happened.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20900px)%20100vw%2C%20900px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyber_bullying_by_ansonn_d2bk6s1-fullview_11zon-1728316288.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22For%20Pritha%20it%20was%20a%20traumatic%20experience%20that%20pushed%20her%20the%20avoid%20social%20media%20for%20a%20while.%20for%20Priya%2C%20to%20be%20am%20influencer%20social%20media%20was%20her%20tool.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyber_bullying_by_ansonn_d2bk6s1-fullview_11zon-1728316288.jpg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyber_bullying_by_ansonn_d2bk6s1-fullview_11zon-1728316288-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyber_bullying_by_ansonn_d2bk6s1-fullview_11zon-1728316288-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyber_bullying_by_ansonn_d2bk6s1-fullview_11zon-1728316288-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyber_bullying_by_ansonn_d2bk6s1-fullview_11zon-1728316288-800x600.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyber_bullying_by_ansonn_d2bk6s1-fullview_11zon-1728316288-600x450.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyber_bullying_by_ansonn_d2bk6s1-fullview_11zon-1728316288-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyber_bullying_by_ansonn_d2bk6s1-fullview_11zon-1728316288-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyber_bullying_by_ansonn_d2bk6s1-fullview_11zon-1728316288-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369041%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFor%20Pritha%2C%20it%20was%20a%20traumatic%20experience%20that%20led%20her%20to%20avoid%20social%20media%20for%20a%20while.%20For%20Priya%2C%20however%2C%20social%20media%20is%20an%20essential%20tool%20for%20becoming%20an%20influencer.%20(Representative%20image)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20what%20happens%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nirali.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ll%20give%20you%20an%20example%2C%20a%20very%20young%20girl%20had%20reached%20out%20to%20us.%20I%20think%20she%20was%2019-20%20then.%20Someone%20was%20sharing%20her%20number%2C%20photographs%2C%20and%20name%20on%20pornographic%20websites.%20Somebody%20created%20a%20profile%2C%20and%20you%20know%2C%20they%20would%20impersonate%20her%20and%20chat%20with%20people.%20She%20started%20getting%20these%20random%20calls.%20So%20she%20reported.%20She%20told%20her%20parents%2C%20and%20they%20went%20to%20the%20police%20station.%20They%20knew%20someone%2C%20and%20the%20profile%20was%20deleted.%20But%20the%20problem%20continued.%20When%20one%20profile%20was%20deleted%2C%20another%20one%20opened%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20girl%20reached%20out%20to%20Nirali%2C%20and%20she%20recalls%20taking%20down%2016%20to%2017%20such%20profiles%20of%20hers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20other%20day%2C%20an%20acquaintance%20sent%20me%20an%20account%20with%20my%20photo.%20It%20had%20my%20face%2C%20but%20it%20was%20a%20nude%3B%20a%20morphed%20picture%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priya%20says.%20But%20the%20number%20of%20times%20Priya%20has%20found%20herself%20in%20such%20instances%20has%20made%20her%20indifferent%20today%3B%20she%20has%20her%20life%20to%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20point%20I%20was%20like%2C%20okay%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20clarify%20it%20on%20my%20personal%20account%2C%20and%20ask%20everybody%20to%20report%20it.%20And%20most%20times%20it%20gets%20deleted%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priya%20says.%20%E2%80%9CI%20checked%20after%20it%20four%20days%20later%20and%20the%20profile%20was%20deleted%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20platforms%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F143543%2Ffacebook-ncw-women-internet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Instagram%20have%20the%20option%20to%20make%20a%20profile%20private.%20Nirali%20says%20that%20it%20is%20an%20important%20preventive%20step.%20But%20for%20some%20people%2C%20a%20private%20profile%20might%20not%20be%20an%20option.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20this%20point%2C%20if%20you%20ask%20me%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20so%20indifferent%20about%20it%20because%20as%20someone%20with%20a%20public%20account%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20make%20my%20account%20private%3B%C2%A0%20I%20do%20aim%20to%20be%20a%20creator.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20the%20account%20to%20be%20private%20just%20because%20people%20can%20misuse%20my%20information%20if%20I%20have%20a%20public%20account%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priya%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20and%20her%20friends%20have%20also%20been%20subject%20to%20becoming%20the%20face%20of%20cyber%20scams.%20Nirali%20explains%20that%20this%20is%20not%20uncommon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHonestly%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20much%20we%20can%20do%20to%20prevent%20it%20because%20of%20the%20freely%20available%20technology.%20See%2C%20I%20believe%20technology%20is%20never%20good%20or%20bad%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20purpose%20for%20which%20you%E2%80%99re%20using%20it%20that%20shapes%20it%20up.%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20(AI)%20is%20a%20wonderful%20thing%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%20we%E2%80%99re%20seeing%20this%20rise%20of%20AI%20images%20and%20stuff%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20organisation%2C%20we%20get%20complaints%20with%20screenshots%20of%20people%20telling%20young%20girls%2C%20%E2%80%98If%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20share%20such%20a%20picture%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20going%20to%20nudify%20your%20image%E2%80%99.%20How%20many%20women%20would%20actually%20go%20and%20complain%3F%E2%80%9D%20Nirali%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriya%20has%20spoken%20to%20some%20of%20her%20fake%20accounts%3B%20not%20the%20ones%20that%20nudified%20her.%20There%20were%20others%20who%20used%20her%20picture%20to%20run%20elaborate%20scams.%20%E2%80%9CLike%2C%20It%20had%20happened%20earlier%20as%20well.%20Somebody%20made%20a%20fake%20account%2C%20with%20a%20bio%20saying%20%E2%80%98vote%20for%20me%E2%80%99%20and%20it%20was%20leading%20them%20to%20a%20spam%20link.%20So%20that%20is%20still%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priya%20says%2C%20elucidating%20how%20the%20volume%20of%20such%20crimes%20can%20make%20it%20difficult%20for%20any%20confirmative%20action%20to%20take%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20never%20got%20flagged%20down%20by%20the%20platform%20despite%20several%20reports.%20And%20a%20lot%20of%20them%20follow%20a%20similar%20pattern.%20Most%20of%20them%20have%20%E2%80%98vote%20for%20me%20in%20this%20link%E2%80%99%20and%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20link.%20It%E2%80%99s%20like%20spam%2C%20where%20they%20can%20hack%20your%20account%20and%20something%20like%20that.%20All%20these%20accounts%20that%20I%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20of%20myself%20and%20my%20friends%20have%20that%20link%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriya%20has%20even%20engaged%20with%20one%20of%20her%20fake%20profiles.%20One%20that%20had%20the%20%E2%80%98vote%20for%20me%E2%80%99%20link.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20I%E2%80%99m%20talking%20to%20the%20person%20on%20the%20account%20who%20has%20my%20pictures%20and%20everything%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20like%2C%20oh%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20participating%20in%20a%20contest%2C%20so%20we%2